You could create a download file, but only in newer browsers.<p>We have an internal application which requires CSV export, we use something like this:<p><pre><code>        csv = cleanTurkishChars(makeCSV(data));
        csv = &#x27;data:application/csv;charset=utf-8,&#x27; + encodeURIComponent(csv);
        $(&quot;#csvexport&quot;).attr({
            &#x27;href&#x27;: csv,
            &#x27;target&#x27;: &#x27;_blank&#x27;
        });</code></pre>
